Package org.uddi4j.transport

Interface Summary
Transport Interface for a SOAP transport to be used by UDDI4J.
 

Class Summary
ApacheAxisTransport Transport implementation for Apache AXIS SOAP stack.
ApacheSOAPTransport Transport implementation for Apache SOAP stack.
HPSOAPTransport Implementation for a SOAP transport to be used by UDDI4J.
TransportBase Partial implementation of Transport interface.
TransportFactory Factory to dynamically create a Transport implementation.
 

Exception Summary
TransportException Represents a communications error originating within the SOAP transport.
